## ğŸ§  **9. Troubleshooting / Scenario-Based**

**Q31. What happens if two people run Terraform apply at the same time?**
â†’ The state file may get corrupted â€” thatâ€™s why we use **state locking** (e.g., DynamoDB lock for S3 backend).

**Q32. Terraform shows â€œdriftâ€. What does it mean?**
â†’ Drift means the actual infrastructure has changed outside of Terraformâ€™s control.

**Q33. How do you update a resource in Terraform?**
â†’ Change the configuration and run `terraform apply`. Terraform updates only the changed parts.

